comments: Hardaway Jr. (DAL) establishes himself in Washington's (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Washington (CHA) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Irving (DAL) after the release.
Both Williams (DAL) and Miller (CHA) make mutual marginal contact with one another while jostling for rebounding position.
Ball (CHA) extends both hands forward and initiates contact to Doncic's (DAL) upper body during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Williams (CHA) moves alongside Doncic (DAL) and marginal contact occurs along the perimeter.
Ball (CHA) aviods making contact to Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) arm during his shot attempt near the rim.
Lively II (DAL) moves alongside Hayward's (CHA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) takes an additional step into Washington's (CHA) path and delivers illegal contact that affects Washington's defensive position.
Miller (CHA) takes longer than 5 seconds to release the inbounds pass.
Williams (DAL) does not release the ball prior to the 24 second shot violation.
Ball (CHA) grabs and holds Irving's (DAL) jersey off ball prior to the inbound pass being received.
Hayward (CHA) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
Ball (CHA) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr (DAL).
